{"word":"ἀλεκτοροφωνία","slug":"ἀλεκτοροφωνία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀλεϰτοροφωνία, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀλέκτωρ\">ἀλέκτωρ</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:φωνή\">φωνή</a></el>] ‘crowing of a cock’ = <b><i>cockcrow, dawn,</i></b> in Roman reckoning the third watch of the night or the period from midnight to 3 hours <b><a href='B:480 13:35'>Mk 13:35</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄλειψαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλέκτωρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}